---
title: Double Spicy Sichuan Beef & Green Bean Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: This easy meal showcases tender beef strips with bold Sichuan garlic paste, sriracha, honey and soy, delivering savoury, sweet and hot all in one bite. Paired with aromatic garlic rice, this flavour-packed dish is perfect for a weeknight dinner or a special treat!
